description: An old hospital on Arran Island, that has been closed for years, is hastily reopened to provide accommodation for the survivors of the “Northern Star” wreck. But the patients begin to disappear, and a police officer, William Hopley, remembers about the local rumors about the cursed hospital of Bran Moor. So, he asks his old friend Maud Nighitingale, the ghost-hunter, and Harlan Draka for help...
name: L'ospedale Stregato

description: A vivid dream bring back Kurjak’s lost son to his own mind… But is it the heart-rending memory of Miklos, who died during a bombing in the Balkan war? Or is it a request for help, strong as the call of blood, coming from another son, one that Kurjak never got to know, who’s now living in faraway, unreachable land? Always standing at his friend’s side, Harlan goes with Kurjak towards the unknown… They’ll find inhumane horrors and near-unreal threats waiting for them!
name: Il figlio di Kurjak

description: A great storm is coming to the town of Winter, Iowa. It could be worse and more destructive of the notorious storm that hit the place 50 years ago, when many of its citizens lost their lives in mysterious circumstances... Harlan and the Amesha, Anyel, go there, too, persuaded that one of their old, demonic adversaries will come back with the storm... And the dark heart of Evil, fated to grow until it will crush the whole community, is concealed in the cellar of the McDougals cursed house...
name: La Lunga Notte dell'Odio

description: A Prague mystery: Ljuba, the girl who became the adoptive child of Harlan and co. and now lives in the Theater of the Lost Steps, is haunted by horrific nightmares and the indelible memory of the evil Thorke. When her attractive maths teacher unveils her own dark alter ego, it’s the beginning of a turmoil of events that will enable Dampyr to finally find out what’s concealed behind the world of the Black Dimension—there, a decisive match between the Amesha and Hell is under way!
name: Nella Dimensione Nera

description: Always ready to side with rebels, Harlan, Kurjak & Tesla find themselves fighting alongside the Black Sentinels against the armies of two infernal commanders: General Zefon and Count Straygor. Harlan fears they will be annihilated, when he finds out that the strategist of the enemy forces is none other than Marshall Vapula, his old teacher of fighting and military tactics at the tenebrous Dark School!
name: Dittatura Infernale

description: Harlan’s Japanese friend, the former yakuza Hasegawa Kenshin, is trying to begin a new life under the identity of a respectable fisherman. By his side, the attractive Keiko, the reincarnation of the woman he had been in love with for centuries. But after Keiko is kidnapped by a commando formed by his ex-enemies, Kenshin goes to Harlan for help. To rescue Keiko, they will have to land on a remote island in the middle of the Ocean and face General Tamasaburo’s legion of diehard fighters. And, alas!, these are not common human soldiers, but invulnerable Han’a demons!
name: I Dimenticati

description: The beautiful Ambra, princess of Gwynedd, reveals her secrets... How could she, a barren Mistress of the Night, conceive a son with a Roman general called Magnus Maximus... How she had raised ina dangerous situation the young Aurelius Ambrosius, whose fate would have been to lead, with his friend Artos, the rebellion in Britannia... What was her relationship with her stepdaughter Severa, who chose to challenge her, becoming Black Annis, the queen of the fierce Tylwyth Teg... And, finally, how she met the Dampyr of the 5th century A.D...
name: Il Segreto di Amber Tremayne

description: Birth and vocation of a Dampyr... Gwion, raised by Keridwen the Sorceress as the herder of her pigs, has grown up with her children, too—the lovely Creirwy and the horrid Morfran. But it will be the young boy, the son of a Master of the Night and a human princess, who will acquire the knowledge contained in the cauldron of Dagda, a late scientist and philosopher who belonged to the Masters’ race... After becoming Taliesin, i.e. “the glowing boy”, he will join his fate with Amber’s and her protégés, Ambrosio and Artos, the liberators of Britannia: together, they will fight against their mother, Severa, queen of the monstrous Tylwyth Teg...
name: Taliesin il Bardo

description: The beautiful Anita Montoya, a brave officer from the Mexican Narcotics squad, witnessed the massacre of a group of policemen by some vicious undead... Luckily for her, a reporter, Raul Barraza, called his vampireslaying friends to help them... A Master of the Night appears to be the leader of a criminal drug cartel and Harlan, Tesla & Kurjak will end up uncovering a conspiracy that has its roots in the Mexican Revolution, a century ago...
name: El Lobo
Un generale, due dritti, due fiocche

description: After saving a baby from the clutches of Calendar Man, Batman is left with more questions than answers. What happened to the Calendar Man? Has a new player entered the game?
name: Scare Tactics Part 1 of 6

description:
Continuing Devon's hit one-shot Killing Dinos 101 from early 2014, where she taught her students how to defend against and hunt dinos, summer break is over and it's time to see what Miss. Cooper, the dino killer extraordinaire has done during the break! Did she hone her skills hunting savage beasts or did she spend the time relaxing in her bikini? Or both? Please join us for Devon's newest color book and see what the lovely yet vicious did during Summer Break!

name: Battleground: Detroit!

description: It's Christmas in war-torn London, and things are about to get even crazier when the woman known as Harley Quinn is unleashed.
name: Combat Part 2 of 9

description: Each of the first four issues of New Zodiax premieres a new character who can channel the energies of the cosmos, making them all instant collector's items! This issue: A tale told in the spirit of the Kaiju, the last bastion of civilization is protected by the New Sagitarius, the colossal lava monster named Multaa! Also inside, the Liberaider is caught between the blood-thirsty Dregs and the mercs for hire Greenback and Pyrotek!

Between the mists of the Scottish Highlands, Harlan Draka and his companions faces what appears to be an ordinary adventure, facing a group of undead that haunt an old castle... But nothing seems to go their way... In a seemingly meaningless chaos, nightmarish creatures appear— the Nocturnal, who can vanish as they please, voodoo dolls pierced through by pins, sphinxes offering puzzles to solve, etc... But the strangest thing of all is that their undead enemies can are unaffected by the sunlight! And the truth is that Harlan, Kurjak and Tesla unwittingly fell into the game of Alel, the Collector, an immortal and invulnerable demigod who owns and rules his own private universe— there, he is almighty and has the power of life, death and transformation over every living creature. To get out of there, our friends will have to ask the help of an attractive she-demon and a flying knight from the pages of Ludovico Ariosto...
name: Il collezionista

description:
Gli orrori di Khara Khoto

Reduced to dust and a few stark ruins, the mythical Khara Khoto sleeps its millenary slumber in the desert of Alashan. A few miles away, though, veiled by illusions, the real Black City lies in the sands, ready to awaken... and filled with horrors!

La palude

In the swamps of Okefenokee, the vampires of the marshes are fighting in a deadly struggle against their predators, Harlan, Tesla & Kurjak. Caught in the middle between the two clashing parties, Roscoe gets to a crossroads of his desperate existence...

Il labirinto del negromante

The park of Château Carignac is cursed. A long time ago, in the exact center of the park there was the Marquis’ hunting pavilion, that burned during the night in 1654. Why does it sometimes reapper, then, right in the middle of the park’s maze? But nobody who saw the pavilion ever came out of the twisting and dark lanes of the garden to tell it...
name: Gli orrori di Khara Khoto; La palude; Il labirinto del negromante

description:
La fiamma di ghiaccio

An innocent girl, who’s been kidnapped by a gang of amateurish criminals, turns out to be an inhumane and twisted creature...

La nebbia

In the core of Massachusetts, an out-of-season mist thickens over the waters of Lake Armanack, a reservoir formed by the Waste Valley Dam... And through it, the Great Ancients are trying to find a gap to attack our reality...

Mogadiscio

Shootings, arm trafficking, attacks... and vampires! One of Kurjak’s old friends summons our heroes to Somalia’s war zone, to fight a powerful Master of the Night!
name: La fiamma di ghiaccio; La nebbia; Mogadiscio
